{"tid":1971264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子旺角街頭捱斬浴血　倒地昏迷　目擊者：斬甩半邊耳仔","createTime":"2020-04-13T19:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T17:29:23.000Z","uid":202340,"like":49,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ac8604ebf00e07d1ef26a2cd06f807b5c1f0f6","tid":1971264,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T19:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4316468/org/b1acf523fe50af79a6b00eb66e0af94e.jpg/NLiGYMkSr5ABcjrx-Ij1GHJsenbK20prMsN6kDLDepA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4316468%2Forg%2Fb1acf523fe50af79a6b00eb66e0af94e.jpg%2FNLiGYMkSr5ABcjrx-Ij1GHJsenbK20prMsN6kDLDepA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=9d98d8d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角奶路臣街發生斬人案。今日晚上10時許，一名年約20至30歲男子途經奶路臣街德發大廈外時，突遭2至3人持刀斬傷，男子背部中多刀、半邊耳朵被削去重傷倒地，不省人事，女性友人在旁呼救，現場遺下大灘血迹及紗布，刀手事後逃去無蹤，救護車趕至現場後，將傷者送院醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n案發後有多名軍裝警員到場，封鎖現場調查事件，案件暫列傷人案。有目擊者指，傷者被斬去半邊耳仔，背部多處中刀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/460437/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%8D%B1%E6%96%AC%E6%B5%B4%E8%A1%80-%E5%80%92%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7-%E7%9B%AE%E6%93%8A%E8%80%85-%E6%96%AC%E7%94%A9%E5%8D%8A%E9%82%8A%E8%80%B3%E4%BB%94?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama&amp;fbclid=IwAR2zL3IQ5JUpzlb9yZLDRbm9x1RV-PlxDRIEhouH4ARCjG3AN20efyojAgw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F460437%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%258D%25B1%25E6%2596%25AC%25E6%25B5%25B4%25E8%25A1%2580-%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7-%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%2596%25AC%25E7%2594%25A9%25E5%258D%258A%25E9%2582%258A%25E8%2580%25B3%25E4%25BB%2594%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama%26fbclid%3DIwAR2zL3IQ5JUpzlb9yZLDRbm9x1RV-PlxDRIEhouH4A